entry.title: test #3
entry.summary: This post from wtogami at apache.org is being flagged as an issue due to the address not being subscribed to the list, which should result in an automatic rejection by the server. If the post manages to go through to the list, it indicates a problem with the configuration. There is also an HTML attachment that has been scrubbed, but no further information is provided regarding its content or relevance to the issue at hand.
